description: Modern and meticulously designed Seaport loft. Soaring high 12'+ ceilings with exposed beams, custom integrated lighting, and tiled feature wall. Curved, decorative teak slat divider separates the main space from an office nook, while maintaining an open concept complete with a built in desk and hidden storage. Custom designed staircase leads up to the lofted bedroom, and a full wall of sound deadening windows in the living room leads out to your exclusive PRIVATE PATIO. Bathroom features a spa-like experience, accented by stone and a glass walled shower, with plenty of closet space. Chef's kitchen with breakfast bar, S/S appliances, and matte stone counters. Enjoy the convenience of laundry in your unit, Nest thermostat, and additional deeded storage locker. This unit can be offered furnished or unfurnished. Virtual tour available.
